573
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ćemo ići na kavu, ali...

574
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pri puno godina Starbucks američki, to su ozbiljne kompanije.

575
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Propaje.

576
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znamen, propo nije me baš briga.

577
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, to su ozbiljne kompanije.

578
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kola je ostali...

579
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I učiš namo ide ono...

580
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tužiš na ispitivati.

581
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drani sve što treba, posadje ekipu veliko da gleda.

582
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su došli sa zaključkom...

583
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, u Hrvatskoj to je nemoguće, ono i sjede piju kavu.

584
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, istina. Oni nisu propali sabve.

585
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, u Hrvatskoj to ne može proći.

586
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zato mi je drago, znaš.

587
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajdi pak idemo si...

588
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kod njih je ono, uzmi kavu i...

589
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da, pa samo ideš pa radiš nešto pa se vraćaš pa put merda.

590
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je baš kao dio naše kulture.

591
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

592
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I neka, ja sam to ponosan.

593
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je štetna, ali ne bez.

594
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možda će se razviti neke dobre ideje na tim kavama.

595
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa većinom se razviju.

596
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa većinom se razviju.

597
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zborimo za nas.

598
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, po meni je kava, ono, ostišta je nekako...

599
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pauzica i nekako vid komunikacije s nekim.

600
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Obično li se neku na kavu, jel?

601
