613
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] A, dobro, opet dobra stvar za prodaj.

614
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je uvijek dobro kada neko radi i bori se,

615
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] a sada, mislim, ako bi trebalo podržati, naravno, da bi podržala,

616
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali, kažem, taj tip muzike i taj tip zabave nije za mene.

617
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam vam radoholičar.

618
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne spomeniš primišlje bez mentala, da nema smisla.

619
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ja sam ponosna.

620
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo nek se događa, nek se širi taj glas

621
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da je primišlje prirodno prekrasno.

622
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

623
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Daj za kraj neku poruku, budućim poljoprivrednicima.

624
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, dođite u moju mailing grupu i idemo lobirati.

625
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

626
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Drugačije ne možemo.

627
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema da, bez.

628
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možemo šutiti, tako da kogod ima neki poljoprivredni problem,

629
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] samo neka mi se javi i rado ćemo o tom porazgovarati i boriti se.

630
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ivana, hvala. Darko, hvala.

631
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, ekipa, vidimo se, čujemo se.

632
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala na pozivu.

633
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Maj drugi put.

634
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav.

635
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bilo bi poželjno.

